{"tid":1283994,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做雙子座真係有苦自己知。。","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T06:18:10.000Z","uid":36435,"like":11,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e73b021e905371f78b5e160305c8fabd2d7aa1","tid":1283994,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"雙子的愛是最永恆的，可以付出一切，有人說我們花心，那時我們沒有真正的愛，當雙子愛上一個人的時候是痛苦的，因為我們太敏感。假如雙子愛上了一個不愛自 己的人，那莫我相信他永遠都不會再愛了，當愛給過了一個人，他再也沒有能力再付出了，其實太多的人都不懂我們，其實連我們自己都不懂自己，我們很會偽裝， 很會說謊，但我們最細膩，對感情最敏感，雙子的愛與悲傷，誰又真的瞭解！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cf4ab9817fdab344f8d0e70b556b1f39d522bf","tid":1283994,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我無野講<br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"a3047025d6025f4493e536c0ef3501a592339828","tid":1283994,"uid":46086,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:57:10.000Z","msg":"弱智才是永恆的"},{"pid":"92d12fe105844f8bf45a10ceccda47333b847bf5","tid":1283994,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"智商有冇50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cbdd67d87d94b13ecfbaa42e74fd61e0c5fe4e","tid":1283994,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"雙子表示認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzfbXtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzfbXtQ.png&h=dd2bba79&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"49677ab6e11daaba1bb7f0869c5101c34f4d5010","tid":1283994,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80cbdd67d87d94b13ecfbaa42e74fd61e0c5fe4e","tid":1283994,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"雙子表示認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"